00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:36,278
Really?

241
00:11:36,529 --> 00:11:38,489
Huh. I guess he just didn't want
to have sex with me.

242
00:11:38,572 --> 00:11:39,698
That's correct.

243
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:41,742
Well, that's fine,
I wasn't that into him anyway.

244
00:11:41,826 --> 00:11:43,994
-Yes, you were.
-Okay, Janet, I have a question.

245
00:11:44,078 --> 00:11:47,248
-Okay.
-What is The Bad Place like?

246
00:11:47,415 --> 00:11:51,335
Oh, sorry, that is the one topic
I'm not allowed to tell you about.

247
00:11:51,419 --> 00:11:56,340
I can only play you a brief audio clip
of what is happening there right now.

248
00:11:56,424 --> 00:11:57,967
Okay.

249
00:11:58,050 --> 00:12:00,010
[people screaming]

250
00:12:00,094 --> 00:12:02,596
[woman] <i>The bear has two mouths!</i>

251
