Well, it doesn't sound awesome.

252
00:12:09,061 --> 00:12:11,480
Does everyone have a huge house except me?

253
00:12:11,564 --> 00:12:13,149
All right, we need a plan.

254
00:12:13,232 --> 00:12:15,860
I say we just lie low
and hope that they don't notice me.

255
00:12:15,943 --> 00:12:17,570
I'm sorry, I don't think I can help you.

256
00:12:17,653 --> 00:12:19,238
I just don't like being dishonest,

257
00:12:19,321 --> 00:12:22,450
and I can't advise you
to be dishonest either.

258
00:12:22,533 --> 00:12:24,994
Come on, I'm just asking
you to fudge a little bit.

259
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:27,413
You must've told a few
white lies in your life.

260
00:12:27,496 --> 00:12:28,956
I mean, what was your job?

261
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:31,500
I was a professor of ethics
and moral philosophy.

262
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:33,711
Mother-forker!

263
00:12:34,128 --> 00:12:35,921
-I'm getting a stomachache.
-[sighs]

264
00:12:36,005 --> 00:12:37,882
I'm in a perfect utopia,

265
00:12:37,965 --> 00:12:40,301
and I'm... I have a stomachache.
This is awful.

266
00:12:40,634 --> 00:12:43,012
I, uh... I think I have to
tell Michael about this.

267
00:12:43,304 --> 00:12:44,472
[Michael] Tell Michael about what?

268
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:46,182
[Eleanor] Michael? Hi.

269
00:12:46,265 --> 00:12:48,058
What have you been up to?

270
00:12:48,142 --> 00:12:52,229
Eleanor, Chidi, I would like you to meet
Tahani and Jianyu.

271
00:12:52,313 --> 00:12:55,065
They are soulmates
and your next-door neighbors.

272
00:12:55,691 --> 00:12:56,817
Hello.

273
00:12:56,901 --> 00:12:59,320
Can I just say I love your house?

274
00:12:59,653 --> 00:13:02,865
It's just so tiny and cute.

275
00:13:02,948 --> 00:13:06,202
It's like a little child's plaything,
like for a family of mice

276
00:13:06,285 --> 00:13:08,329
or for a very fancy little dog.

277
00:13:08,412 --> 00:13:11,957
I love it. It's just so sweet and teensy.

278
00:13:12,208 --> 00:13:14,293
Just like you. Boop.

279
00:13:14,376 --> 00:13:15,544
-Oh!
-Oh!

280
00:13:15,711 --> 00:13:17,254
You booped me. [laughs]

281
00:13:17,338 --> 00:13:18,797
-I did.
-That's fun.

282
00:13:19,048 --> 00:13:20,633
Tahani and Jianyu are having a little

283
